### NextWatch API - Sample Requests

## Test Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/health

### Seed Popular Movies (One-Time Setup - ~2-3 minutes for 500 movies)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/seeder/seed-popular-movies

### Test Recommendation Request (after seeding completes)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "selectedMovies": ["Inception", "Interstellar", "The Matrix"],
  "maxRecommendations": 5
}

